
1.Data Binding BR is not Found
Solution:
apply plugin: 'kotlin-android'
    apply plugin: 'kotlin-android-extensions'
    apply plugin: 'kotlin-kapt'

abdroid{
 dataBinding {
        enabled = true
    }
    }
2. Without calling findViewById. call directly by Id
Solution :
import kotlinx.android.synthetic.main.activity_main.*

3.Cannot fit requested classes in a single dex file (# methods: 109441 > 65536)
Sol :
  defaultConfig {
    multiDexEnabled true
  }

